This website is meant to be an aid to study the good Bible. 
It is my believe that this is the inspired word of God.

I don't follow any particular translation or christian denomination. 
I just want to understand the Bible as best as I can, and share that understanding with others.

Being truthful and honest is most important to me and I will try to be as accurate as possible in my explanations.
But I am not perfect and I may make mistakes. 
If you find any errors, please let me know so I can correct them.


